<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | SmartBuild Ltd</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f111a; /* Dark theme to match your system */
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1d29 0%, #0f111a 100%);
        }

        .error-card {
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .display-1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #0dcaf0, #007bff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .btn-outline-primary {
            border-color: #0dcaf0;
            color: #0dcaf0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-outline-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0dcaf0;
            color: #000;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(13, 202, 240, 0.4);
        }

        .brand-text {
            color: #0dcaf0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="error-container">
    <div class="text-center error-card">
        <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold">404</h1>
        
        <div style="height: 3px; width: 60px; background: #0dcaf0; margin: 15px auto; border-radius: 10px;"></div>
        
        <h3 class="text-white fw-bold mb-3">PAGE NOT FOUND</h3>
        
        <p class="text-secondary mb-4">
            The resource you are looking for at <span class="brand-text">SmartBuild Ltd</span> <br> 
            might have been removed or is temporarily unavailable.
        </p>
        
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-primary px-4 py-2 fw-bold">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i> LOGIN TO ACCESS SYSTEM
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-link text-secondary text-decoration-none small">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Go Back
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>